Frontend Folder Structure Rules for Bun Theory

Stack:

* NextJS App Router
* Typescript
* TailwindCSS
* shadcn/ui

Folder Rules:

1. Routes must live in /app.

2. Public ordering pages:

app/

* page.tsx
* menu/page.tsx
* order/page.tsx

3. Admin pages must live under:

app/admin/

Example:

app/admin/dashboard
app/admin/orders
app/admin/menu

4. UI components must live in /components.

Component categories:

components/menu
components/order
components/admin

5. shadcn components must stay inside:

components/ui

6. API calls must be inside:

/services

Example:

services/orders.service.ts
services/menu.service.ts

7. Reusable hooks must live inside:

/hooks

8. Global types must live in:

/types

9. Global utilities must live in:

/lib

10. Cart state must live in:

/store/cart.store.ts

UX Rules:

* Mobile first
* Simple checkout
* Large call-to-action buttons
* Minimal form inputs

Components must be reusable and typed.

